\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20190,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/01\/20\/last-man-to-enter-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":13571,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Paradise: Story of the last man to enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 20, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, I know who will be the last to come out of the Hellfire and the last to enter Paradise. He is a man who will come out of the Hellfire crawling. Allah will say to him:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1068,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/10\/28\/all-jannah-but-refuse\/","url_meta":{"origin":13571,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: All Muslims enter Paradise but those who refuse","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 28, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Everyone from my nation will enter Paradise but those who refuse.\" They said, \"O Messenger of Allah, who will refuse?\" The Prophet said, \"Whoever obeys me enters Paradise, and whoever disobeys me has refused.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src